<a href="/articles/26878.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/26878/indexMediumPc2/26878.jpg?1463360513" alt="今日娱乐：淘宝电影完成 A 轮融资，愤怒小鸟票房不错">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/3/medium/3.png?1411569578" alt="娱乐">
			<span>娱乐</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">今日娱乐：淘宝电影完成 A 轮融资，愤怒小鸟票房不错</h1>
